Hadson Corp said it has signed adefinitive agreement to acquire 85 pct of the outstandingcommon stock of Seaxe Energy Corp.    The company said it will buy the 85 pct interest in Seaxefrom shareholders owning restricted or controlled shares forless than 200,000 Hadson common shares.    It said closing is subject to the approval of titleassignments by the French government.  Seaxe is involved in oiland natural gas exploration and development in the Paris Basinof France. Reuter&#3;